For different products, price per value differs. But some of them sometimes dont make sense.

For example with bread the usual metric for price for value is price/kg. Makes sense but I personally dont like having tiny breads. 

Id like 1 whole bread for lunch or 2 max. Not 50 tiny bread slices.

